import { StyleSheet } from 'react-native'

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
    inscription: {
        alignSelf: 'stretch',
        backgroundColor: '#73B479'
    },
    logo: {
        alignSelf: 'stretch',
        width: 250,
        height: 140,
        margin: 'auto'
    },
    textInput: {
        alignSelf: 'stretch',
        backgroundColor: '#73B479',
        height: 40,
        width: '70%',
        marginBottom: 20,
        color: '#fff',
        borderBottomColor: 'white',
        borderBottomWidth: 2,
        placeholderTextColor: 'white',
        margin: 'auto'
    },
    button: {
        alignSelf: 'stretch',
        textAlign: 'center',
        backgroundColor: 'white',
        marginTop: 30,
        width: 150,
        height: 50,
        margin: 'auto',
        padding: 15,
        borderRadius: 40
    }, 
    btnText: {
        alignSelf: 'stretch',
        color: 'black',
        fontWeight: 'bold'
    },
    textConnect: {
        alignSelf: 'stretch',
        marginTop: 20,
        color: 'white',
        textAlign: 'center',
        textDecorationLine: 'underline'
    }
})

export default styles
